bilizalonak tekinti? Aczel szerint a korrupcio ellenere sok orszagban viragzik a gazdagsag, de azt elhallgatja, hogy Magyarorszagon a korrupcio olyan merteku, amely a felviragzast eleve kizarja, nem beszelve arrol, hogy a korrupt orszagokban is rendkivul erosen lepnek fel a nemzet szovetet roncsolo gengsztervilag ellen. Horn persze olyan vezercikkirot erdemel, mint Aczel es az ot sajtokonferenciara invitalo olyan MUOSZ-t, amelynek vezetoje a Vico-fele gengszterbirodalom egyik lapjanak foszerkesztoje is, es amelynek vezeto szerkesztoje egy Ungvari Tamas, akinek mar a neve maga is olyan jelzo, amelyet tovabbi jelzokkel fokozni sem lehet.=TARGY: NYOMOZAS MEGSZUNTETESE[Magyar Forum, majus 16.]"Horn Gyula karosult (3-as ut, Saab-9000 vezetoules + vodka) tartoskoponyaserulest szenvedett magyar allampolgar, foglalkozasa: jelenleg miniszterelnok -- jogkorei az SZDSZ altal elvonva --, nyomozast inditvanyozott az ELToNT HIVATAL utan. Allaspontja szerint e Hivatal megtalalasa eseten visszaall az az altala rendnek tartott allapot, amelyet rosztovi diakeveiben volt szerencseje tapasztalni.Nyomozas elrendelese iranti kerelmet nevezett szemelyes okokkal isalatamasztotta. Allaspontja szerint a megtalalt -- kiasott? -- Hivatalfelallitasa eseten Kiss Elemer miniszterelnoksegi allamtitkaron kivulnaponta meg legalabb 4-5 szemely szamara adhat ki parancsokat, amire kisse serult lelkiallapota es dr. Torgyan Jozsef allando zaklatasai kovetkezteben feltetlenul szuksege van. Ez szamara raszorultsagi alapon jaro egyeszsegugyi szolgaltatas volna, amelyet egyebkent az SZDSZ kovetelesere annak idejen o maga volt kenytelen eltorolni.A Hivatal a maga napi negy-ot kiadhato parancsaval, kisebb-nagyobb fogaszati muteteivel maga volna az Uj Elvonokura. A jajgatasok es a nyogesek beszuremlese fiatalitolag hatna a karosultakra. Az Uj Elvonokura olyan Elvonokura, amely vegre nem elvonassal, hanem juttatassal -- egy kis hatalommal -- gyogyitana.A nyomozas kezdemenyezoje szerint valaha volt ilyen Hivatal. Es nyomozott is. O emlekszik erre. Voltak POZITIV EREDMENYEK. A kezdemenyezo ezen emlekeit tiszteletben kell tartanunk. De semmi elerzekenyules! Ketsegtelen ugyan, hogy a pozitiv nyomozasi eredmenyeket a Belugyminiszterium leveltaraban tevekenykedo NYILVANOSSAG KLUB ES A TORTENELMI IGAZSAGTETEL BIZOTTSAG nagyreszt lenyelte mar, megis fennall a veszelye annak, hogy MASOKIS emlekeznek, megpedig a pozitiv eredmenyek MASIK oldalarol. Ezert a nyomozas kezdemenyezojet nem szabad ingerelni. Ra kell hagyni a dolgot. Kadereink, ujsagiroink emeljek ki a kezdemenyezes pozitiv vonasait es a jo szandekot. Nepunk lassa, hogy a miniszterelnok jo szandeku. Ember. Egy kis polgar, aki lehetne akar kispolgar is. Ma mar ez nem szegyen!SO"TT, elvtarsak!Allaspontom szerint azonban a miniszterelnok altal inditvanyozott nyomozas nem teljesitheto. Mert a Hivatal es a nyomozas, mint olyan, az ugynevezett rendszervaltas soran szunt meg, de nem azert, hogy legyen rendszervaltas, hanem azert, hogy ne legyen. Ezt akkor meg a panaszos is tudta. A fonyomozok es a fizikai eroszakot alkalmazok -- KOROMLE', TALPSIMOG', VESEMASSZ' STB. -- mar korabban "C"-VONALRA mentek, bankot alapitottak, ugyvedi irodakat nyitottak -- ...and Partners -- es utobb beepultek az olajuzletbe. Tudja ezta miniszterelnok ur is, hiszen fizikailag maga is kilepett a kotelekbol.Jelenleg az allomany legtobb tagja milliardos. Sajat gorillakkalrendelkeznek. Meg a feleseguk utan sem tudnak mar szemelyesen nyomozni, inkabb leisszak magukat, ha kudarcot vallottak. Igy a Hivatal felallitasa abba a nehezsegbe utkozik, hogy nekik maguknak kellene onmaguk utan nyomozniuk vagy nyomoztatniuk.Ezenfelul a tisztelt miniszterelnok urnak azt is kellene -- illenek --tudnia, hogy a feketegazdasag ellen o, a szocialista, mar nem kezdhetnyomozast, mert mar a szocialista szavazok tulnyomo resze is leszorult a feketepiacokra: az adozott arakat mar ok sem tudjak megfizetni. Ha aztan a nep a feketepiaciokon nem jut olcsobb arukhoz, valamint, es nem utolsosorban, ha fekete munkajaval -- "ahogy lehet" -- nem jut realberhez, akkor fellazad. Es vajon mit ostromol meg? A FEKETE Gazdasagat! Ez pedig nemzetkozi bonyodalmakhoz vezet, mert FEKETE JANOSEK gazdasaga/gazdagsagavegyes. A fele Le, a masik fele uni. (Leumi.) Horn Gyulanak tudnia kellene, hogy a KET-UTLEVELESEK LETHELYZETET NEM TEHETJUK KOCKARA.A miniszterelnok ellenvetese, miszerint a lazadas leverese nem jelentene akadalyt -- "Csinaltam en ezt mar, gyerekek!" --, nem veheto komolyan, mivel meg az o legjobb baratja, Vladimir Meciar sem kenyszerult eddig konkret lazadas leveresere, es o, ha be akar kerulni a szocdem internacionaleba, vegul is nem kovetheti Romaniat a magyarveresben.Ez hagymazas lehetoseg, es csak vegso megoldaskent szabad elkepzelni. De ott meg nem tartunk. Hala Kis Janos emberjogi kuzdelmenek.A fentiek alapjan az el sem kezdett, de tobbszor beigert NYOMOZASTMEGSZUNTETEM. A rendortabornokok fizetese a nyomozas kilatasba helyezese kovetkezteben beallt ijedtsegukre valo tekintettel 30% halapenzzel novekszik, a tiszthelyetteseke ugyanennyivel csokken.Kelt mint fent.KUNCZE GABORbelugyminiszter"Lattam: OK!Brown ormesterTaszarA masolat hiteleul:Nev es cim a lap impresszumaban=DEMOKRATA (20)Sugarut az alban szocializmusba: Segelyek: szegenyektol csorog a penz a meg szegenyebbekhez?(Szarka Sandor irasa)   Rikito ruhaba oltozott no harsog a buszon: "Tudod, dragam, en nem tudok elhelyezkedni. De minek is dolgoznek?" Hosszan sorolja, hogy honnan milyen segelyt kap, a vegen kijon vagy harmincezer. A jarmuben hirtelen elfogy a levego, ahogy a  tobbiek osszeneznek. A gyarban ok 25 ezret keresnek.  A gondoskodo allam idoszakaban termeszetesek voltak a juttatasok. A dolgozok csak a toredeket kaptak meg annak, amit megtermeltek, de cserebe az allam lakast huzott fel a fejuk fole, tamogatta a tejet, a kenyeret, biztositotta a nyaralasat, tanittatta a gyerekeit, olcson adta a villanyt, es minden mas alapveto  ellatasi cikket. Az allam elvett az emberektol, hogy aztan josagosan visszaadjon szinte mindent. Gazdasagi alaptetel, hogy a jovedelmek nagymerteku elvonasa es szetosztasa nem hatekony, mivel ellustitja az embereket. Sulyos szocialis okok persze megmagyarazhatjak e lepest, azonban a 70-es evekben mindenki visszakapott mindent, igy a nagymerteku ujraelosztasnak nyilvanvaloan nem volt meg  az ertelme. Hacsak nem az, hogy az embereknek nyilvan nem jut eszukbe megkerdojelezni azt a rendszert, melynek a szubvenciokon es a juttatasokon keresztul ok is latszolagos haszonelvezoi. Minden harmadik forint Ma mar csak segelyezettek vannak. A szubvenciokat a 80-as evek vegeig nagyreszt felszamolta a kormany, megis a berek semmivel nem kerultek kozelebb a tizszeres osztrak szinvonalhoz. Az arak annal  inkabb. A tamogatasok csokkentesere nem azert kerult sor, mert az allam mersekelni akarta  jovedelem-ujraeloszto szerepet, inkabb csak azert, mert a visszaeso termelesbol es a csokkeno munkasletszambol a korabbiaknal kevesebb adobevetelt lehetett kipreselni. A terhek tehat valtozatlanok  maradtak, ellenben nott az olyan retegek szama, akiknek semmit nem sikerult visszakapni az allamtol. A munkanelkuliseg novekedese tetejebe tovabbi allami forrasokat kotott le. Igy allhatott elo az a furcsa helyzet, hogy a fizetesekbol valo elvonast tekintve Magyarorszag tovabbra is a masodik helyen van  Europaban. Az elso helyezett svedeknel a GDP 60 szazaleka kerul ujraelosztasra, nalunk ez az arany 57  szazalekos. Az atlagos magyar csalad minden harmadik forintja allami csatornakon keresztul erkezik.Pedig a szabad gazdasagok sokkal hatekonyabbak. A kozelmultban Vito Tanai es Ludger Schuknecht-az elmult 100 ev tapasztalatainak vizsgalata utan-a The Economistban azt allitotta, hogy az allami  kiadasoknak nem szabad meghaladniuk a GDP 30 szazalekat. Az ennel nagyobb merteku elvonas mar  rontja a gazdasag hatekonysagat, a tulzott elvonasok nem osztonzik fejlesztesre a vallalatokat, a tulzott adok a feketegazdasag fele taszitjak a munkaadokat es a munkavallalokat is. Ott, ahol a koltsegvetesi kiadasok meghaladjak a GDP 50 szazalekat, a feketegazdasag aranya 11 szazalek korul van, az ennel csekelyebb kormanyzati szerepvallalasu orszagokban viszont csak 6 szazalekos (Magyarorszagon 30 szazalekra becsulik). A tulzott ujraelosztas ugyanakkor a munkamoralt is rombolja. A befizeto retegek es  a haszonelvezo retegek jovedelme tul kozel kerul egymashoz. A munkanelkuliek csak eletszinvonaluk  csekely javulasara szamithatnak akkor, ha munkaba allnak, ez pedig inkabb a kiskapuk megkeresesere osztonoz. Kulonosen akkor, ha a segelyek megtartasa mellett munkat talalhatnak a feketegazdasagban is.  Hogy mindez nem csak elmelet, azt jol mutatja, hogy jelenleg Svedorszagban is a gazdasag ellustulasanak a megallitasa, es a 10 szazalek koruli koltsegvetesi deficit lefaragasa van napirenden.Magyarorszagon a segelyek szetosztasat az onkormanyzatok vegzik, azonban allami szabalyozas hatarozza meg, hogy mi az a minimalis ellatas, amit minden onkormanyzatnak biztositani kell. A magyar lakossag a kovetkezo cimeken juthat rendszeres penzellatashoz: tappenz, terhessegi gyermekagyi segely, gyermekgondozasi dij, oregsegi nyugdij, rokkantsagi nyugdij, oregsegi jaradek, munkakeptelensegi  jaradek, ozvegyi nyugdij, vegkielegites, szuloi nyugdij, ozvegyi jaradek, baleseti tappenz, rendszeres szocialis jaradek, banyaszok egeszsegkarosodasi ellatasa, rokkantsagi jaradek, nemzeti gondozottak  penzbeli ellatasa, gyermeknevelesi tamogatas, munkanelkuliek jovedelempotlo tamogatasa, apolasi dij, rendszeres szocialis segely. Ezenkivul szokas, hogy a jelentosebb aremelesek utan a kormany kompenzaciot allapit meg a legelesettebb retegek szamara, amire szinten az onkormanyzat gyujti be az igenyeket. Ellenorizhetetlen igenylok A kotelezo ellatasok mellett a keruletek -anyagi lehetosegeikhez merten-tovabbi segelyeket oszthatnak  szet a raszorulok kozott.Gyermeknevelesi tamogatast az kaphat, aki legalabb harom kiskorut nevel, es  az egy fore eso jovedelem a csaladban kisebb, mint az oregsegi nyugdijminimum (9600 Ft)  haromszorosa. A GYET az oregsegi nyugdijminimum osszegevel egyezik meg. Jovedelempotlo tamogatasert a munkanelkuli segely lejarta utan lehet folyamodni. Az erre jogosultak ket even at az  oregsegi nyugdij 80 szazalekat kapjak kezhez. Lakasfenntartasi tamogatasert azok fordulhatnak, akiknel a lakasfenntartasi koltsegek elerik az osszjovedelem 35 szazalekat, es az egy fore juto havi jovedelem nem haladja meg a nyugdijminimum duplajat. Atmeneti segelyt az kerhet, aki a letfenntartast  veszelyezteto rendkivuli elethelyzetbe kerul vagy letfenntartasi gonddal kuzd. Adhato alkalmankent es  havi rendszeresseggel. Emellett meg apolasi dijert es temetesi segelyert is lehet az onkormanyzatokhoz fordulni. A penzben kifizetettek mellett lehetoseg van termeszetbeni segelyek igenybevetelere is, mint koztemetes, kozgyogyellatas, gyermekek napkozbeni ellatasa, etkeztetes, hazi segitsegnyujtas, csaladsegites, idosek gondozasa, hajlektalanok, idosek, es gyermekek atmeneti otthona, vagy rehabilitacios intezmenyek igenybevetele.A fovarosi keruletek kozul a VIII.-ban van a legtobb kerelmezo penzbeli segelyekre. A kerulet tavaly 35 ezer kifizetest teljesitett, es-Skulteti Jozsef szocialis osztalyvezeto elmondasa szerint-az atmeneti segely a legnepszerubb. Az onkormanyzat minden negyedik forintjat erre forditja, hiszen manapsag igazan nem nehez valakinek bebizonyitnia, hogy letfenntartasi gondokkal kuszkodik. A keruletben amugy 17-fele tamogatas letezik, ennek egyharmada a penzben kifizetett segely. Lehetne tobb is, ugyanis itt van a hajlektalanellato kozpont, marpedig a keruletben tartozkodo hajlektalanok ellatasa szinten az  onkormanyzat feladata. Ugyanakkor a munkanelkuliseg is az atlagnal jobban sujtja a keruletet, es itt van a fovaros leglerobbantabb lakoovezete is. Az onkormanyzat iden 100 millio forintos hitel felvetelere  kenyszerult csak a penzbeli segelyek kifizetesere. Tagadhatatlan ugyanakkor, hogy a segelyek elosztasa nem megnyugtato. Egy reszet jogosulatlanul veszik fel, mikozben sok valoban raszorulo idos ember szegyell kerni, es meg akkor sem jelentkezik, ha mar az ehenhalas kuszoben van. Az o felderitesukre a kerulet sajat megfigyelorendszert hozott letre, a visszaeleseket azonban nagyon nehez felfedezni. A bevallott lakaskorulmenyeket nincs apparatusuk ellenorizni, mint ahogy arra sincs ralatasuk, hogy hogyan alakulnak az elettarsi kozossegek. Gyakran elofordul, hogy kulonbozo keruletekben lako szulok  mind a ket onkormanyzattol felveszik ugyanazokra a gyerekekre a tamogatast. Az osztalyvezeto szerint nagy szukseg lenne egy egyseges informacios rendszerre, ami nemcsak a keruletek kozott mukodne, de  magaban foglalna a kulonbozo egyhazakat, tarsadalmi szervezeteket is. Ezektol ugyanis szinten jelentos osszegeket szakitanak le a segelyakrobatak.Csepelen tobb a penz, vagy kisebb a tulekedes. Balogh Gyongyi szocialis referens szerint itt parhuzamosan akar tobb segelyt is igenybe lehet venni, es a tamogatasokbol akar tobb is osszejohet, mint amennyi a csalad rendes evi jovedelme. A tamogatasok mellett az onkormanyzat vegzi az allami kompenzaciok szetosztasat is. A viz, a csatorna kompenzaciora havonta 400 forint, a futesre pedig ujabb 400 forint adhato. A HTO- aremeles ota-helyi rendelet alapjan-a kerulet jelentosen tamogatja a mas futesre atallni kivanok torekveseit is. Aki vezetekes gazra valt, annak koltsegeibol 100 ezer, mas esetben 40 ezer forintot vallal at az onkormanyzat. A tovabbra is HTO-val futok a futes koltsegenek 25-30  szazalekos visszateritesere szamithatnak.   Ut az alban szocializmusba   A XV. keruletben 400 millio forinttal gazdalkodhatnak. Mint Kovacsne Markus Eva, az Ujpalota- Rakospalotai Onkormanyzat Szocialis vezetoje elmondta, ennek kb. fele megy el a penzbeli tamogatasokra. Itt is letezik futesi tamogatas, ilyen cimen maximum 6-szor 5 ezer forintot kaphat valaki egy evben. Az osztalyvezeto ketkedve hallgatja a kerdest, amely a bevezetoben idezett autobuszos beszelgetesre celoz. Tapasztalatai szerint a segelyekbol-a keruletben legalabbis-maximum 15 ezer  forint szedheto ossze havonta. Az ennel magasabb osszegek csupan annak koszonhetok, hogy a tamogatott tobb gyermeket tart el, ebben az esetben viszont a penz is megoszlik koztuk. Visszaelesek persze itt is vannak. Megfelelo szamitogepes nyilvantartas nincs, az igenyloket nev alapjan tartjak nyilvan, igy elofordult mar olyan is, hogy a kozos lakasban elo nepes csalad minden tagja felvette a sajat nevere pl. a lakasfenntartasi tamogatast. A legtobb esetben csak a kerelmezo sajat bevallasara tamaszkodhatnak az anyagi korulmenyeit illetoen. Az ugyfelek autojarol vagy mas keruletben levo  telkerol, hazarol nincs lehetoseguk informaciokat szerezni, mint ahogy a jovedelmek kozul is csak arrol  szerezhetnek tudomast, amit az illeto az APEH-nak bevallott. Bar az igenylok "buntetojogi felelosseguk tudataban" nyilatkoznak, valojaban semmi kovetkezmenye nincs a felretajekoztatasnak. A jogi procedura  koltseges es hosszadalmas, igy az onkormanyzat meg a napvilagra kerulo visszaelesek utan sem alkalmazza a visszakovetelest sot, a jelenlegi jogszabalyok meg azt sem teszik lehetove, hogy kizarjak a segelyezhetok korebol azokat, akik korabban jogosulatlanul vettek fel tamogatast.Persze nem a segelyek tenyevel van a baj, csak Magyarorszagon valahogy osszekuszalodott az egesz.  Sokaknak talan faj ez a kijelentes, de ugy tunik, Magyarorszagon tul magasak a segelyek, vagy annyira rossz az elosztasuk, hogy az indokoltnal jobban megterhelik a tarsadalmat. Az elvonasok csokkentesevel mindenkeppen novelni kellene a bereket, mivel 6-7 ezer forint tobbletert nem erdemes elmenni dolgozni. Akkor inkabb-ahogy neha hallani lehet-ehen doglik az ember, de meg inkabb kiskapuk utan nez.Mar az atlagosan fizetett munkas is belecsuszik a 44 szazalekos adosavba, es ha lesz vagyonado,  biztos, hogy a 35 negyzetmeteres lakasa es a Trabantja utan is fizetni kell. Kenyszeru logika: fokozodo elvonasok a szegenyektol, hogy lehessen adni a meg szegenyebbeknek. Lassan igy minden kiegyenlitodik, mindenki raszorulo lesz, tompa, az allamon csungo szerencsetlen. Agrolszakadt valtozata a hetvenes eveknek.Vagy mi most az alban szocializmust epitjuk?  =REGIONALIS HIREKCOMMUNISTS DENOUNCE MEDIA "FALSIFICATIONS" . . . Communist campaign manager and Duma deputy Valentin Kuptsov on 21 May denounced what he described as "false" documents that have appeared in the press recently. He particularly criticized Komsomolskaya pravda for publishing on 15 May what it claimed were excerpts from the Communists' economic program and Moskovskie novosti, which in its 19-26 May issue published an allegedly Communist document concerning plans to overturn President Boris Yeltsin's 1991 decree banning political activity in the workplace. -- Robert Orttung in Moscow---WHILE THE RUMOR MILL CHURNS ON. Kuptsov and Communist leader Gennadii Zyuganov also denied widespread reports of discord during an 18 May Communist Central Committee meeting, ITAR-TASS reported on 21 May. For instance, Izvestiya ran the implausible scenario that Zyuganov was about to make a deal with Yeltsin, and deliberately lose the election in exchange for being appointed to the post of prime minister. Rumors about conflict within the Communist Party (KPRF) are published almost daily in the anti-Communist press, which includes independent publications such as Izvestiya and Moskovskii komsomolets as well as official newspapers like Rossiiskaya gazeta and Rossiiskie vesti. The rumors generally highlight more extreme elements within the KPRF, presumably in order to frighten swing voters. At the same time, reports depicting Zyuganov as ready to sell out or compromise are aimed at driving a wedge between him and his Communist supporters. -- Laura BelinCANDIDATES HAVE TROUBLE FINALIZING PROGRAMS. Both President Yeltsin and Zyuganov have had considerable difficulty issuing detailed versions of their electoral programs. Yeltsin's most recent plan was to issue his campaign platform by 20 May, but he did not meet his self-imposed deadline. One of his campaign managers, Sergei Filatov, said that he thought it would appear soon but that the staff needed at least two more days to finish it. Duma member Tatyana Koryagina, who is working on the Communists' economic platform, also said that it would take her team a few more days to iron out the main points of the opposition's proposals. She reassured reporters that private property would be respected and that price and foreign exchange controls would not be reimposed. -- Robert Orttung in MoscowPERRY WARNS RUSSIA, UKRAINE NOT TO SEND SS-18 TECHNOLOGY TO CHINA. It would be a "significant mistake" if either Russia or Ukraine were to provide SS-18 strategic missile technology to China, U.S. Secretary of Defense William Perry told reporters at the Pentagon on 21 May. Perry had revealed Chinese interest in the SS-18 in a Washington Times interview. The SS-18 is the largest intercontinental ballistic missile in the world. Built at the giant Pivdenmash plant in Ukraine, the SS-18 formed the backbone of the Soviet strategic rocket force. While Russia still deploys 186 of them, they would be eventually banned under the START II treaty. Perry said that other than making the missile's booster available for space launches, any transfer of SS-18 technology would violate the START I treaty and the Missile Technology Control Regime. -- Doug ClarkePRESIDENTIAL AIDE: RUSSIA WILL "WRECK" NATO EXPANSION. In an interview with Ekho Moskvy on 21 May, President Yeltsin's foreign policy aide, Dmitrii Ryurikov, condemned plans to expand NATO as "unwise, shortsighted, and irresponsible," saying Russia "is doing everything to wreck it." Ryurikov, apparently frustrated that repeated Russian offers of some sort of compromise have been snubbed, said he hoped "common sense would prevail," but that "for now there is little sign of this happening." He blamed NATO's inflexibility for the deadlock on the issue, claiming the alliance has no "serious thoughts" about cooperation with Russia. Meanwhile, at a conference in Dublin, Deputy Foreign Minister Sergei Kyrlov repeated earlier compromise offers, saying Russia could accept East European countries joining NATO political but not military structures. He also urged these countries to consider Ireland, which belongs to the EU, but not NATO, as a possible model. -- Scott ParrishRUSSIA HAILS IRAQI-UN OIL DEAL. Foreign Ministry spokesman Grigorii Karasin described the recently-signed agreement between the UN and Iraq as "a breakthrough," ITAR-TASS reported on 21 May. Under the deal, Iraq, which is still under a UN economic embargo imposed after its 1990 invasion of Kuwait, will be allowed to sell $2 billion worth of oil to purchase food and medicine under UN supervision. Karasin added, however, that Russia views the deal as a "temporary measure" which "does not replace the main task of fully unblocking" the embargo. While all members of the UN Security Council supported the deal, Russia and France hope it will foster progress toward fully lifting the embargo, while the U.S. and Britain have a more guarded stance. Iraq owes Russia about $7 billion, which it cannot repay until after the embargo is lifted. -- Scott ParrishRUSSIAN CRIMINALS AN INTERNATIONAL THREAT. Police officials from Europe and North America attended the third international seminar on organized crime in the former Soviet Union in London on 20-21 May, ITAR-TASS reported. The seminar was organized by Britain's National Criminal Intelligence Service. Valerii Serebryakov, from the Chief Directorate for Organized Crime, reported that there are 5,000 criminal gangs in Russia with 32,000 members, 100 of them with international operations. Extortion and money-laundering feature prominently in their activities. Maj. Gen. Giovanni Verdicchio of the Italian Financial Guards said the Italian Mafia is investing in privatized businesses in Russia. Meanwhile, in Moscow NTV reported on 20 May that Boris Fedorov, the president of the National Sports Foundation and the Natsionalnyi Kredit Bank, was arrested after drugs were found at his home. Fedorov is an associate of Shamil Tarpishchev, President Yeltsin's tennis coach and a co-founder of the National Sports Foundation. -- Peter RutlandMURDER WAVE. The number of murders in Russia rose from 15,500 in 1990 to 32,000 in 1995, Trud reported on 18 May. Many of them involve the division of the market economy spoils: last year, there were 500 contract killings, of which only 61 were solved. "We live in conditions of criminal terror," the report concluded. While 73% of murders in the country are solved--slightly more than in the U.S.--only 40% are solved in Moscow. The paper also noted that 2,447 murders were committed in Kazakhstan in 1995, which in proportion to the population is about half the Russian rate. In the latest round of a mafia turf war in Moscow, three members of the "Kazan gang" were shot dead on 20 May while standing outside a restaurant near the luxury Olympic Penta hotel, AFP reported. -- Peter RutlandRUSSIA APPLIES FOR OECD MEMBERSHIP. Russia became the first former Soviet republic to apply for membership in the 27-country OECD, Western agencies reported on 21 May. Russia also requested entry into OECD's affiliates, the Nuclear Energy Agency and the International Energy Agency. In December 1995, the Czech Republic became the first former socialist country to join the OECD. OECD officials privately suggest that Russia is a long way from meeting the club's membership criteria. Russia has also applied to join seven working groups of the Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation Organization (APEC), ITAR-TASS reported on 22 May. World Bank President James Wolfensohn arrived in Moscow on 22 May to discuss loans of $350 million and $500 million for highway renovation and coal industry reconstruction. -- Natalia GurushinaPOLES ON RUSSIAN PRESIDENTIAL ELECTION . . . A recent public opinion poll conducted by the Warsaw-based Public Opinion Research Center (OBOP) shows that 42% of Poles over the age of 15 are anxious about the outcome of the presidential elections in Russia next month. Only 7% of respondents were "hopeful" about the outcome, with 24% saying they were not interested and 20% declaring indifference. Of the respondents, 59% believed that Russia would like to subordinate Poland to Russian rule; only 23% did not believe this was the case, Gazeta Wyborcza reported on 22 May. -- Jakub Karpinski--AND CZECHS ON CZECH-GERMAN DECLARATION. More than 55% of the respondents in a recent opinion poll say they would accept a Czech- German declaration in which the Czechs admitted the "moral incorrectness" of the expulsion of some 3 million Sudeten Germans from Czechoslovakia after World War II if the Germans gave up property claims and compensated Czech victims of the Nazi regime. Conducted by the Factum agency and published in Mlada Fronta Dnes on 22 May, the poll revealed that such a declaration would be unacceptable to only 30% of the respondents. Previous polls have indicated that an overwhelming majority of Czechs are opposed to an official apology for the expulsion; the Factum poll used the term "admitting moral incorrectness." According to the poll, those who experienced World War II and those with leftist views are more likely to oppose any settlement of the Sudeten German issue, while young people tend to be more pragmatic. -- Jiri PeheSLOVAK PRESIDENT'S SON REACTS TO POLICE DECISION. Michal Kovac Jr. on 21 May issued a statement to TASR responding to the police's decision the previous day to adjourn the investigation into his kidnapping. He wrote that, "I do not wish for anyone, even those who would rather believe in lies, to experience such an approach of the state to its citizen [as I have]." Alluding to his father, he noted that "this state has tried to discredit its citizen in every way possible in order to remove from office another citizen, coincidentally the first citizen of this state." In an attempt to reach its aim, the state "tried to use the police in order to discredit [Kovac Jr.] and put him in prison," even utilizing "the services of individuals with a criminal past," he argued. -- Sharon FisherSLOVAK CABINET SUES SLOVAK JOURNALIST. The government on 21 May announced that a law suit has been filed against Sme editor Peter Toth and its publisher for "intolerance and gross and ungrounded attacks against the cabinet," TASR reported. The government is demanding a public apology and compensation "for the damage to civic honor and human dignity." Toth, who has closely covered the kidnapping of President Michal Kovac's son, has been a frequent victim of criticism from coalition representatives. He was physically attacked last October. The current charges stem from Toth's statements at former policeman Robert Remias's funeral, when he accused the Slovak Information Service and government circles of involvement in Remias's death. Sme chief editor Karol Jezik told CTK that the suit is "an attempt at intimidation," adding that the cabinet has already filed more than ten lawsuits against Sme and its editors. -- Sharon FisherHUNGARIAN FIGHTER PLANES LEAVE FOR POLAND WITHOUT PARLIAMENT'S APPROVAL. Hungary's armed forces have sent MiG-29 aircraft to Poland for military exercises without the approval of the parliament, Hungarian media reported on 22 May. The Hungarian Army's official 1996 schedule provided for the deployment of eight MiG fighters to Poland on 16 May, but the parliament did not give its approval by that date. The planes were reportedly sent to Poland without even the approval of Defense Minister Gyorgy Keleti. Magyar Hirlap quotes the constitution as stating that the armed forces cannot cross the country's borders without the prior consent of parliament, except in the case of military exercises within the framework of international treaties or peacekeeping activities carried out at the request of the United Nations. The five opposition parties on 21 May unanimously demanded the dismissal of Keleti. -- Zsofia SzilagyiHUNGARY TO GRANT COMMON LAW RIGHTS TO HOMOSEXUAL COUPLES. The parliament on 21 May amended the Civil Code to grant common law rights to homosexual couples, Hungarian media reported. Homosexuals are now entitled to inherit property from their partners and receive a deceased partner's pension. But they will not be allowed to adopt children. The amendment was required after a Constitutional Court ruling in March 1995 extending recognition of common-law relationships to homosexual couples. -- Zsofia SzilagyiNATO NOT TO HUNT DOWN KARADZIC? Atlantic Alliance sources on 21 May said that IFOR troops will not go after Karadzic for fear the move could lead to casualties among the peacekeepers, Onasa reported. The head of the Hague-based war crimes tribunal, Justice Richard Goldstone, said however that he cannot "believe that 60,000 [IFOR] troops would have difficulty" in arresting the war criminals, The New York Times noted on 22 May. Meanwhile in Washington, State Department spokesman Nicholas Burns said the U.S. has spoken to Serbian President Slobodan Milosevic about his obligation to make sure the Bosnian Serbs observe all aspects of the Dayton accord, including bringing war criminals to justice. Milosevic reportedly told the Americans that he wants the Bosnian Serbs to comply, but he did not say what he will do about it, Onasa added. Burns also called Karadzic's plans for a referendum "a lot of hot air," adding that "it won't happen because we won't let it happen," Reuters stated. -- Patrick MooreNATO TROOPS TO PARTICIPATE IN JOINT MILITARY MANEUVERS IN ROMANIA. At the request of President Ion Iliescu, the Chamber of Deputies on 21 May approved the participation of NATO troops in six joint military exercises to be held on Romanian territory this year within the framework of the Partnership for Peace program, Radio Bucharest reported on the same day. Socialist Labor Party deputy Silviu Somacu vehemently opposed the proposal, raising arguments described by Adevarul as "typical of communist propaganda." Some deputies called him a "dirty Communist," and fist-fight was narrowly averted, Evenimentul zilei reported. -- Michael ShafirRECORD ECONOMIC GROWTH IN ALBANIA. According to an IMF report, Albania continues to be the poorest European country, but its economy is the fastest-growing in Europe, AFP reported on 21 May. The report states that the economy grew by 11% last year, while the budget deficit was 7% of GDP and annual inflation only 6%. Foreign investment amounted to $2.5 billion, and remittances from Albanians working abroad reached $400-600 million. However, wages remain low--at an average of $70 a month--and unemployment is still widespread. The Frankfurter Rundschau on 22 May reported that official unemployment is 15% but soars to almost 50% in the former industrial regions in the north. -- Stefan KrauseThis material was reprinted with permission of the Open Media  Research Institute, a nonprofit organization with research offices in  Prague, Czech Republic. For more information on OMRI publications,  please write to:  info@omri.cz
